This Morning host Holly Willoughby, 41, led the glamour as she arrived at Royal Ascot today. The mum-of-three showcased her toned physique in a pink number while out at the race course. Holly teamed the look with a quirky rose-strewn hat, pink bag and nude sandals. The ITV favourite continued Royal Ascot tradition, as she teamed her outfit with an eye-catching headpiece.